  "title": "TacoCraft",
  "description": "Adds Tacos to Minecraft Fabric 1.15.2+! ",
  "body": "<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"187\" height=\"63\" /></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/PZpbnMc/Taco-Craft.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1105\" height=\"182\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>A Minecraft Fabric 1.15.x&nbsp; to 1.16.x mod adding several new types of special tacos!</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>-=*=-</strong></em></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/536626891755487256/697257705143795712/2020-04-07_21.29.25.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1124\" height=\"615\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'arial black', sans-serif;\"><b>Adds tacos to Minecraft!</b></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'arial black', sans-serif;\">Tacos on 1.2.0:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">- Steak Taco</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">-Carnitas Taco</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">-Al Pastor Taco</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">-Fish Taco</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">-Chicken Taco</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">-Cheesy Taco</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">-Crunchy Taco</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">-Golden Taco</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'arial black', sans-serif;\">This mod also adds:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">-Corn Crop: IMPORTANT: Right click when done growing instead of destroying it to get a piece of corn!&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">-Brick Furnace</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">-Comal</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">-Tortillas</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">-Crunchy Shell</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'arial black', sans-serif;\">Wiki:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10px; font-family: 'arial black', sans-serif;\">Need to learn how to play with the mod? Recipes, tutorials, and more are here!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/franiscoder/TacoCraft/wiki/TacoCraft\">https://github.com/franiscoder/TacoCraft/wiki/TacoCraft</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">And here is another wiki:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\"><a href=\"https://modwiki.miraheze.org/wiki/TacoCraft\">https://modwiki.miraheze.org/wiki/TacoCraft</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'arial black', sans-serif;\">Bugs:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'arial black', sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Please report bugs on the Github page. You will need to make an account.&nbsp;</span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://github.com/franiscoder/TacoCraft/issues\">https://github.com/franiscoder/TacoCraft/issues</a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'arial black', sans-serif;\">Images:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px;\">Check the images tab!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'arial black', sans-serif;\">Credits:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Author: ffrann</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Artist: TacomonkeyC32 (Comal Block)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Taco Trader:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/Linguardium/WanderingTradesmen\">https://github.com/Linguardium/WanderingTradesmen</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Check out this lib to make your own tradesman!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;\">Thanks to the helpers in #mod-dev on the Fabricord for helping me!&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><em><strong>CHECK OUT MY NEW MOD, GOLEMS GALORE!&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/golems-galore\" rel=\"nofollow\">https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/golems-galore</a></strong></em></p>",
